    "question_id" : 79704290,
    "title" : "How do I run java test suites in parallel with Gradle",
    "body" : "<p>I'm using the relatively new test suite plugin from Gradle: <a href=\"https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/jvm_test_suite_plugin.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/jvm_test_suite_plugin.html</a>.</p>\n<p>I assumed that the different test suites, including the default <code>test</code> task would run in parallel, but that doesn't seem to be the case? How can I get my <code>test</code> and <code>integrationTest</code> suites to run in parallel?</p>\n",
