    "answer_id" : 79706179,
    "question_id" : 79704290,
    "body" : "<p>Set the <code>maxParallelForks</code> for both <code>test</code> and <code>integrationTest</code></p>\n<p>You can find more about it <a href=\"https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/performance.html#a_run_tests_in_parallel\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>Or if you want to run <code>test</code> and <code>integrationTest</code> simultaneously set</p>\n<pre><code>org.gradle.parallel=true\n</code></pre>\n<p>in your <code>gradle.properties</code> file. <a href=\"https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/performance.html#sec:enable_parallel_execution\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">docs</a></p>\n",
